  "title": "v2: AlgoliaSearchHelper events not handled from widget methods",
  "body": "**Do you want to request a *feature* or report a *bug*?**\r\n*bug*\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\nListening for events (`helper.on`) within a widget's `init` method does not work. Worked in v1.\r\n\r\n- jsFiddle with 2.0.0.beta.5: https://jsfiddle.net/timkelty/ufaycett\r\n- same jsFiddle, but with 1.x latest: https://jsfiddle.net/timkelty/4s70qkq0/\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\n2.0.0.beta.5",
